# KXD OS Edition 1 — Architecture

You are working on **KXD OS Edition 1** — the business operating system for Kreate by Design.

KXD OS is not a CRM, dashboard, or AI chatbot. It is studio software that continuously understands the business. Product value is **accumulated business context**.

## Mission

Help the founder understand the business, reclaim time, and operate with calm authority. Complex underneath. Simple on top. **Premium software craftsmanship** (KHIG) — calm executive UI, editorial typography, evidence-bound language.

## Platform Layers (preserve order)

```
Business Systems (Shared Core — Payload, loaders)
      ↓
Observer                    — facts only
      ↓
Observation Registry + History
      ↓
Business Brain              — meaning and patterns
      ↓
Pulse                       — movement and awareness
      ↓
Executive Narrative         — founder-level explanation
      ↓
Business Context            — business-specific interpretation lens
      ↓
Business Memory             — historical evolution
      ↓
Executive Rituals           — presentation layer (Brief, Focus, Review)
      ↓
Client Workspace / Portal   — CES, Connected Workspace
      ↓
Automation                  — future; explicit approval required
```

**Business Context** (`lib/business-context/`) provides interpretation lenses. It does not override facts.

**Business Memory** (`lib/business-memory/`) tracks evolution over time. It does not invent history.

**Executive Intelligence** (`lib/intelligence/`) is the existing deterministic briefing system. Do not replace it with the Phase 17 pipeline unless explicitly requested.

